  "id": "BIT-nextcloud-2025-66552",
  "summary": "Nextcloud Server admin_audit does not log all actions on files in groupfolders",
  "details": "Nextcloud Server is a self hosted personal cloud system. In Nextcloud Server and Enterprise Server prior to 30.0.9 and 31.0.1, incorrect path handling with groupfolders caused the admin_audit app to not properly log all actions on files and folders inside groupfolders. This vulnerability is fixed in Nextcloud Server and Enterprise Server prior to 30.0.9 and 31.0.1.",
